# Azure App Service vs Azure Functions

| Feature | Azure App Service | Azure Functions |
|----------|-------------------|-----------------|
| Service Type | PaaS | Serverless (FaaS) |
| Best For | Web Apps, APIs | Event-driven tasks |
| Server Management | No | No |
| Scaling | Manual or Auto Scale | Automatic |
| Billing | Based on App Service Plan | Pay per execution (Consumption Plan) |
| Runs Continuously | Yes | Only when triggered |
| Typical Use Cases | Websites, REST APIs | Automation, scheduled jobs, event processing |
| Supports Deployment Slots | Yes | No (Functions themselves do not use deployment slots in the same way as Web Apps) |
| Example | E-commerce website | Resize uploaded images automatically |
